description: Category describing the wiring diagram of the setup.

name.description: Name of the schema used to describe the wiring diagram.

node_database.description: Link to database with nodes. e.g. devices.json

edge_database.description: Link to database with edges e.g. connectors.json

node_database_version.description: Version of the database with list of nodes.

edge_database_version.description: Version of the database with list of edges.

nodes.description: List of dictionaries describing name and type of nodes. e.g. [{"name": "MSR", "mtype": "object"}]

edges.description: List of dictionaries describing name and type of nodes. e.g. [{"from": "Screen", "to": "human_agent", "mtype": "Attachment"}]

code.description: Link to code used to prepare and manage the diagrams.
